      "start_ts": 0,
      "end_ts": 0,
      "en": "I was so exhausted because obviously I didn't sleep the night before because I was so nervous about the event.",
      "zh": "我真的特别累，因为前一天晚上根本没睡着，那个活动让我觉得很紧张。",
      "phonetic_us": "/aɪ wəz soʊ ɪɡˈzɔstɪd bɪˈkɔz ˈɑbviəsli aɪ ˈdɪdənt slip ðə naɪt bɪˈfɔr bɪˈkɔz aɪ wəz soʊ ˈnɜrvəs əˈbaʊt ði ɪˈvɛnt/",
