    {
      "sentence_id": 3,
      "episode_id": 250,
      "episode_sequence": 3,
      "start_ts": 0,
      "end_ts": 0,
      "en": "And because I'm naturally shy and quiet, that doesn't come easily to me.",
      "zh": "但因为我本身性格比较害羞、安静，这对我来说不是容易的事。",
      "phonetic_us": "/ænd bɪˈkɔz aɪm ˈnæʧərəli ʃaɪ ænd ˈkwaɪət, ðæt ˈdʌzənt kʌm ˈizəli tə mi/",
